  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="top" height="1" width="33">５</td>   
    <td align="center" valign="top" height="1" width="137"><a href="Search2.exe?Code=tz6dbsownceptcjp32&dMode=0&KeyWord=&searchMode=1&keyMode=10&fromYear=%97%DF%98a+5%94N&fromDate=%97%DF%98a+5%94N+6%8C%8E%92%E8%97%E1%89%EF%81i%91%E63%93%FA+6%8C%8E15%93%FA%81j&tillYear=%97%DF%98a+5%94N&tillDate=%97%DF%98a+5%94N+6%8C%8E%92%E8%97%E1%89%EF%81i%91%E63%93%FA+6%8C%8E15%93%FA%81j&speaker=%90%5B%90%85%97%B2%8Ei&speaker1=%90%5B%90%85%97%B2%8Ei&speaker2=&speaker3=&eTarget=1&AhitResult=%8C%9F%8D%F5" target="_top">深水　隆司</a><br> 
      （新和会）</td>
    <td height="1" width="500"> 
    都市公園について<br>
    　１　東野公園について<br>
    　（１）現状について<br>
